actions.message:
>Play <name/link> | Plays the <name/link> in the voice channel (you must be in a voice channel)
>Stop | Stops the music
>Pause | Pauses the music
>Resume | Resume the music
>Skip | Skips to the next music
>Queue | Shows you the list of music that are in queue
actions.name: Add Embed Field

actions.message:
>Kick @user <reason> | Kicks the user with the reason you've given
>Ban @user <reason> | Bans the user with the reason yoU've given
>Purge <amount> | Purges the <amount> of messages in the channel it has been fired in (user has to have manage messages permission)
>Warn @user <reason> | Warns the user for the reason given (you need to have administrator permissions)
>Warns @user | Shows the warns of the user
>ClearWarns @user | Clears the user's warns (you need to have administrator permissions)
actions.name: Add Embed Field
